          "type": "text",
          "text": "6. Performance Considerations"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Scalar functions in SQL Server can have performance implications, especially when used in large queries or applied to many rows. The main considerations include:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
