        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "The function's performance is generally acceptable for small to medium-sized datasets, but care should be taken when applying it to large tables or in complex queries."
